ViewObject.Name: PVTSearchRVO
ViewObject.SQLQuery: SELECT PVT_SEARCH.PVT_HDR_SEQ, PVT_SEARCH.Request_log_seq, PVT_SEARCH.PVT_Num, PVT_SEARCH.Plate_Id, PVT_SEARCH.PVT_SOURCE, PVT_SEARCH.Contra_code, PVT_SEARCH.Obsrv_seq, PVT_SEARCH.Cust_ID, PVT_SEARCH.Sector_Code, PVT_SEARCH.Tariff_ID, PVT_SEARCH.PI_ID, PVT_SEARCH.HHC_ID, PVT_SEARCH.PVT_date_time, PVT_SEARCH.PVT_VHCL_geo_lat, PVT_SEARCH.PVT_VHCL_geo_lon, PVT_SEARCH.PVT_Status_ID, PVT_SEARCH.PVT_STAGE_ID, PVT_SEARCH.ENFORCE_STAGE_ID, PVT_SEARCH.CLOSURE_REASONS, PVT_SEARCH.CLOSURE_REMARKS, PVT_SEARCH.CONTRA_AMT, PVT_SEARCH.Discount_amt, PVT_SEARCH.PVT_AMT_PAYABLE, PVT_SEARCH.PVT_AMT_PAID, PVT_SEARCH.verified_by, PVT_SEARCH.verified_date, PVT_SEARCH.DEF_City_Code, PVT_SEARCH.DEF_Country_Mst, PVT_SEARCH.ADP_number, PVT_SEARCH.Appeal_number, PVT_SEARCH.court_case_number, PVT_SEARCH.zone_code, PVT_SEARCH.Disc_Period_end_date, PVT_SEARCH.Created_By, PVT_SEARCH.Created_Date, PVT_SEARCH.Updated_by, PVT_SEARCH.Updated_date, PVT_SEARCH.Country_Code, PVT_SEARCH.Foreign_Plate, PVT_SEARCH.PLATE_NUMBER, PVT_SEARCH.PLATE_CNT_ID, PVT_SEARCH.PLATE_CTG_ID, PVT_SEARCH.PLATE_TYPE_ID, PVT_SEARCH.VEH_MAKE_ID, PVT_SEARCH.VEH_MODEL_ID, PVT_SEARCH.VEH_COLOUR_ID, PVT_SEARCH.Active_Flag, PVT_SEARCH.Blacklist_flag, gim.CUST_NAME customer_name, gim.Mobile_num Mobile_num FROM (SELECT pvth.PVT_HDR_SEQ, pvth.Request_log_seq, pvth.PVT_Num, pvth.Plate_Id, pvth.PVT_SOURCE, pvth.Contra_code, pvth.Obsrv_seq, pvth.Cust_ID, pvth.Sector_Code, pvth.Tariff_ID, pvth.PI_ID, pvth.HHC_ID, pvth.PVT_date_time, pvth.PVT_VHCL_geo_lat, pvth.PVT_VHCL_geo_lon, pvth.PVT_Status_ID, pvth.PVT_STAGE_ID, pvth.ENFORCE_STAGE_ID, pvth.CLOSURE_REASONS, pvth.CLOSURE_REMARKS, pvth.CONTRA_AMT, pvth.Discount_amt, pvth.PVT_AMT_PAYABLE, pvth.PVT_AMT_PAID, pvth.verified_by, pvth.verified_date, pvth.DEF_City_Code, pvth.DEF_Country_Mst, pvth.ADP_number, pvth.Appeal_number, pvth.court_case_number, pvth.zone_code, pvth.Disc_Period_end_date, pvth.Created_By, pvth.Created_Date, pvth.Updated_by, pvth.Updated_date, vpm.Country_Code, vpm.Foreign_Plate, vpm.PLATE_NUMBER, vpm.PLATE_CNT_ID, vpm.PLATE_CTG_ID, vpm.PLATE_TYPE_ID, vpm.VEH_MAKE_ID, vpm.VEH_MODEL_ID, vpm.VEH_COLOUR_ID, vpm.Active_Flag, vpm.Blacklist_flag from Pvt_Header pvth, Veh_Plate_Mst vpm where pvth.Plate_Id=vpm.Plate_Id) PVT_SEARCH LEFT OUTER join (select inst_id as cust_id,INST_NAME as CUST_NAME,''as Mobile_num from GEN_INSTITUTION_MST union select cust_id,first_name as CUST_NAME,Mobile_num from GEN_customer_MST)gim on gim.cust_id = PVT_SEARCH.cust_id
